---
// GitOpsToolCompare.astro — ArgoCD vs FluxCD
---
<div class="gtc-wrap">
  <h3 class="gtc-title">ArgoCD vs FluxCD</h3>
  <div class="gtc-table">
    <div class="gtc-row gtc-row--h"><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--nm">Feature</span><span class="gtc-c">ArgoCD</span><span class="gtc-c">FluxCD v2</span></div>
    <div class="gtc-row gtc-r1"><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--nm">UI</span><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--good">Beautiful web dashboard</span><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--meh">CLI only (Weave GitOps for UI)</span></div>
    <div class="gtc-row gtc-r2"><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--nm">Multi-cluster</span><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--good">Built-in, central management</span><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--good">Per-cluster agents</span></div>
    <div class="gtc-row gtc-r3"><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--nm">Config tools</span><span class="gtc-c">Helm, Kustomize, Jsonnet</span><span class="gtc-c">Helm, Kustomize</span></div>
    <div class="gtc-row gtc-r4"><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--nm">Sync strategy</span><span class="gtc-c">Manual or auto sync</span><span class="gtc-c">Always auto-reconcile</span></div>
    <div class="gtc-row gtc-r5"><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--nm">RBAC</span><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--good">Granular project-level</span><span class="gtc-c">K8s native RBAC</span></div>
    <div class="gtc-row gtc-r6"><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--nm">Image update</span><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--meh">ArgoCD Image Updater</span><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--good">Built-in image automation</span></div>
    <div class="gtc-row gtc-r7"><span class="gtc-c gtc-c--nm">Learning curve</span><span class="gtc-c">Medium</span><span class="gtc-c">Higher (CRD-heavy)</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="gtc-rec"><strong>Pick ArgoCD</strong> if you want a dashboard and multi-cluster from day one. <strong>Pick FluxCD</strong> if you prefer CLI-first, GitOps-native image automation, and tighter K8s integration.</div>
</div>
<style>
  .gtc-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .gtc-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .gtc-table{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .gtc-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:120px 1fr 1fr;gap:8px;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:6px;align-items:center}
  .gtc-row--h{border-bottom:1px solid #334155;padding-bottom:8px;margin-bottom:4px}
  .gtc-row--h .gtc-c{color:#64748b;font-size:.6rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.3px;font-weight:700}
  .gtc-row:not(.gtc-row--h){opacity:0;animation:gtcIn .3s ease forwards}
  .gtc-r1{animation-delay:.05s}.gtc-r2{animation-delay:.1s}.gtc-r3{animation-delay:.15s}.gtc-r4{animation-delay:.2s}.gtc-r5{animation-delay:.25s}.gtc-r6{animation-delay:.3s}.gtc-r7{animation-delay:.35s}
  @keyframes gtcIn{to{opacity:1}}
  .gtc-c{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.68rem}.gtc-c--nm{color:#e2e8f0;font-weight:700;font-size:.7rem}
  .gtc-c--good{color:#4ade80}.gtc-c--meh{color:#f59e0b}
  .gtc-rec{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.6;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.15);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #334155}.gtc-rec strong{color:#06b6d4}
</style>
